description: High Farm is an innovative urban farm founded in 2019, focusing on sustainable food production through vertical farming techniques. By cultivating microgreens, edible flowers, and greens in controlled environments, High Farm aims to bring fresh, pesticide-free produce closer to urban consumers. The initiative emphasizes harmony between technology, nature, and society, promoting gastronomic diversity while minimizing environmental impact. With a commitment to research and development, High Farm aspires to be a leader in sustainable agricultural practices in Latin America.
name: High Farm
